            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1637085548879-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1637085548879-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and cut the <strong>carrots</strong> into batons</p><p>Peel and cut the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into wedges</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637085554270-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637085554270-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637085554270-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637085554270-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1637085554270-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>carrot batons</strong>, <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>red onion wedges</strong> and <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Pour over the<strong> spice rub</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637085560961-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637085560961-x400.jpg",
