            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 25-30 min or until the chickpeas are golden and the vegetables are tender - this is your <strong>Moroccan-style chickpea, carrot & tomato tray bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
